	node js installation + first application
	================================

	step 1:
		open vs code
	step 2:	
		file --> open folder
		choose your folder or create new folder.

	step 3:
		select folder
		open
	step 4:
		goto terminal
	step 5:
		set path your folder.

	step 6:
		> npm init

		>npm install http
	step 7:
		> md pgmfolder
		>cd pgmfolder
	step 8:

		create js file inside pgmfolder

		ex: simple.js

	step 9: type program

	step 10: run program
		goto terminal :

		> node filename.js

		don't close
	step 11:
		goto browser
		http://127.0.0.1:yourportnumber
	OR	
		http://localhost:yourportnumber
 
